									</div>
									<div class='col-14 col-sm-12 col-md-6 offset-sm-1 offset-md-4'>
										<div class='ImageCaption'>Prepare the engines. It’s going to be a long journey. /// Triple-A Metaverse Work in Progress /// Immersive Unreal Engine 5 Experience.</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
											
																				<div class='Block ArticleBlockText'>
							<div class='container'>
								<div class='grid'>
									<div class='col-14 col-sm-10 col-md-6 offset-sm-2 offset-md-4'>
										<div><p>Every journey starts with a question, and in this case, our efforts have been informed by this one: How can we showcase the essence of Star Atlas through SCREAM?</p>
<p>To be fair, we also asked ourselves the following:</p>
<p>Is this game actually fun?
Can players play this over and over?
Are we focusing on ship utility?
Is the game logic and game state hosted on-chain?
You can see how constructing our ‘simple’ game is no easy task. Yet, we challenged ourselves to develop a concept that would embrace the key aspects of a true Star Atlas game as laid out in our original <a href="https://staratlas.com/assets/pdfs/white-paper.pdf">White Paper</a> and <a href="https://staratlas.com/economics-paper.pdf">Economics Paper</a>.</p>
<p>Put another way: SCREAM will be a blockchain-native multiplayer game complete with economic, political, and strategic elements. This will be the first time that players can use their ships to fight for the future of their faction with fun, active, repeatable, on-chain gameplay with earning potential.</p>
<p>Even this definition might be lacking because, as we hope to demonstrate, SCREAM will be an enticing challenge, requiring tough choices, coordination, and strategic thinking from our players on both a faction and regional level.</p>
<p>Without further adieu, let’s take a tour of SCREAM’s context, game loops, and structures.</p>
<p>P.S. We believe this will give enough material for many Atlas Brews!</p>
<h3>Overview — The Context of Scream</h3>
</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>

						</div>

					
																				
												<div class='Block ArticleBlockImage'>
							<div class='container'>
								<div class='grid'>
									<div class='col-14 col-sm-12 col-md-8 offset-sm-1 offset-md-3'>
																														<div class="imageContainer PopInEnable"
											 data-image-url='//images.ctfassets.net/2kg7h835bpe1/49UDH4QbGQqJxaRR1vZEI3/ea5c8f997166d69aa7234ffa9640ef7f/whispers-of-war.png?'
											 data-image-caption='Whispers of war can be heard everywhere in the galaxy /// Triple-A Metaverse Work in Progress /// Immersive Unreal Engine 5 Experience'
											 data-image-width='875'
											 data-image-height='446'
										>
											<div class='imageInner' style='padding-bottom: 50.971428571429%'>
												<picture>
													<source data-srcset="//images.ctfassets.net/2kg7h835bpe1/49UDH4QbGQqJxaRR1vZEI3/ea5c8f997166d69aa7234ffa9640ef7f/whispers-of-war.png?w=862&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=85 862w, //images.ctfassets.net/2kg7h835bpe1/49UDH4QbGQqJxaRR1vZEI3/ea5c8f997166d69aa7234ffa9640ef7f/whispers-of-war.png?w=1724&amp;fm=webp&amp;q=85 3068w"
															type="image/webp">
													<source data-srcset="//images.ctfassets.net/2kg7h835bpe1/49UDH4QbGQqJxaRR1vZEI3/ea5c8f997166d69aa7234ffa9640ef7f/whispers-of-war.png?w=862&amp;fm=jpg 862w, //images.ctfassets.net/2kg7h835bpe1/49UDH4QbGQqJxaRR1vZEI3/ea5c8f997166d69aa7234ffa9640ef7f/whispers-of-war.png?w=1724&amp;fm=jpg 3068w"
