									<div class='col-14 col-sm-10 col-md-6 offset-sm-2 offset-md-4'>
										<div><p><strong>ABOUT STAR ATLAS</strong></p>
<p>Star Atlas is a next-gen gaming Metaverse emerging from the confluence of state of the art blockchain, real-time graphics, multiplayer video game, and decentralized financial technologies.</p>
<p>Real-time graphics technology using Unreal Engine 5’s Nanite allows for cinematic quality video game visuals. Blockchain technology using the <a href="https://c212.net/c/link/?t=0&amp;l=en&amp;o=3518016-1&amp;h=2748636143&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fc212.net%2Fc%2Flink%2F%3Ft%3D0%26l%3Den%26o%3D3397231-1%26h%3D2982849003%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fsolana.com%252F%26a%3DSolana&amp;a=Solana">Solana</a> protocol establishes a largely serverless and secured gameplay experience. Non-fungible tokens obtained and traded within Star Atlas create an economy that replicates the tangibility of real world assets and ownership. To learn more, visit <a href="https://c212.net/c/link/?t=0&amp;l=en&amp;o=3518016-1&amp;h=1530369193&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fc212.net%2Fc%2Flink%2F%3Ft%3D0%26l%3Den%26o%3D3397231-1%26h%3D3652583731%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstaratlas.com%252F%26a%3DStarAtlas.com&amp;a=StarAtlas.com">StarAtlas.com</a>, join a faction at <a href="https://c212.net/c/link/?t=0&amp;l=en&amp;o=3518016-1&amp;h=3921988929&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fc212.net%2Fc%2Flink%2F%3Ft%3D0%26l%3Den%26o%3D3397231-1%26h%3D445912205%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fplay.staratlas.com%252F%26a%3DPlay.StarAtlas.com&amp;a=Play.StarAtlas.com">Play.StarAtlas.com</a> and send your spaceships on a deep space mission by enrolling them into a Faction Fleet.</p>
